text: I LIKE YOU MOST 보고 알게 된 아티스트. 소속사에서 정말 각잡고(?) 공들인 퀄리티의 곡들 보고 깜짝 놀랐어요. 텐님이 얼마나 유명해질지 궁금합니다. (청량큐티날티섹시..) 나열하니 이상하지만 제가 생각하는 텐님의 이미지입니다. 이런 컨셉을 언젠가는 보고 싶은 소망이 있습니다. 약간 남자판 아틀란티스 소녀 바이브의 태국스러움도 한 스푼 담긴 습하고 쨍한 여름 바다, 푸르른 들판 아래 활기찬 싱그러운 청춘의 느낌을 풀어내는 텐의 이미지가 문득 궁금해집니다.

text:
ขอแนะนำรายการที่เตนล์ของพวกเราไปออกนะคะ ทุกคนตามไปดูความน่ารักกันได้ (มีซับไทยทุกรายการค่ะ)
- Key & TEN talk and stage รายการ the seasons : กราบพี่คีย์ shinee งามๆสำหรับรายการนี้ที่ทำให้ทุกคนรู้จักเตนล์มากขึ้นกับเพลงดีๆ พี่ชอบหนูที่สุดเลย ของพล เชษฐ
- My Neighbor Charles : เป็นไดอารี่ที่ตามถ่ายตั้งแต่รายการ the season ไปจน fan concert ทั้งที่เกาหลี ที่ไทย เปิดบ้านเตนล์กับน้องแมวที่เกาหลี และก็บ้านที่อบอุ่นที่ไทย
- TEN bubble bubble    : รายการนี้เตนล์เป็น host เปิดอีพีด้วยการทำอาหารให้เมมเบอร์
- king of mask singer TEN ช่อง mbc world เพลง all of my life

author: @lionofjudah5221
text:
How to have eternal Life

1. Believe that you have sinned (done wrong) and that Jesus can save you.
"All have sinned and have fall short of the glory of God" 
Romans 3:23.

2. Ask God to forgive you and make your heart clean in Jesus name.
"If we confess our sins, He is faithful and just to forgive us our sins and to cleanse us from all unrighteousness" 1 John 1:9

3. Tell Jesus that you want him to be Lord of your life (that you will serve him).
"If you declare that Jesus is lord, and believe that God brought him back to life, you will be saved" Romans 10:9.

4. Trust Jesus to set you free from wanting to sin and to give you a new life that will never end.
"Now you have been freed from sin and have become God’s servants. This results in a holy life and, finally, in everlasting life"
Romans 6:22

author: @markys99
text: Omg I'm actually crying here- I'm so excited and happy to see that FINALLY Ten will truly have his long-awaited solo debut. I knew from the beginning that he would be one of NCT's first soloists, but seeing it actually happen is still surreal for me. I've always maintained that Chittaphon is one of the greatest idols that kpop has ever had the honor of having. He is simply and LITERALLY one of the most complete idols in kpop, like, there is NOTHING he can't do, and when I say that, I mean it, very seriously, and if you know even a little about his various abilities, you know that "Ace" is the perfect word to describe him. Ten is truly a perfect artist, and I'm so happy, proud and excited to see him finally debut solo. His previous songs are my passions, so I'm so excited about the album. Ten, FIGHTING! Love you!💚💚💚🛐🛐🛐

author: @valenti.nana.i
text: Today was my birthday, I didn't have the best day, it felt empty and the only thing that genuinely made me happy was the fact that Ten dropped this song, just hearing your voice is enough to me, seeing your beautiful smile, the way you act, this video is so pretty and comforting in a lot of senses despite the slightly sad meaning of the song, I'm in love with the song already and I cannot wait to hear the full version and the whole album, really, as a 10vely this was the best gift I could ever receive, I'm always proud of you TEN but this time I can't even express how insanely proud I am of you and your art, passion and work you put on every single time and this is just the start of your solo career, more many things will come and the world will bow down to you as the most talented idol in kpop ever Idc if I'm rambling at this point it's just the facts !!! anyways you're fucking amazing Ten Lee and I can't believe you're finally debuting I'm just emotional after so many years you deserve this so so so much and I'm sure this album is going to be sick and you'll end the whole industry king I love you with my whole life

author: @fknxrose
text: In NCT Ten's new song, the dream sequence unfolds with him starting alone in an empty car, purchasing just one ticket before a mysterious girl appears. The symbolism points to a solo journey or experience, emphasized by the lone ticket purchase. The girl's sudden presence adds a layer of significance, perhaps representing companionship or a pivotal relationship. The dream takes an intriguing turn in the last scene as the girl disappears, leaving Ten alone in the parking lot. This twist suggests a fleeting or transient nature to the connection or experience, leaving room for interpretation. The dream sequence serves as a compelling narrative device, inviting listeners to explore the symbolic and abstract elements embedded in the story.

author: @poiiana3363
text:
I am so emotional right now.. i wanna cry in my shower 
- the song is so good. I could play it on repeat 
- the vocals 10 out of ten
- the vdo and graphics is so aesthetic and classy and the vibe is great. Like a movie 
- the chemistry between them is great. Always wanted to see ten with girls 
- his acting, the way he look at her like she means so much and the loneliness when she’s gone
- the lyrics, you can interpret it differently. It could mean a impossible love. A break up song. Or a song that says we fanclub and artist wont last forever. Let’s enjoy it now. Either way it hurts. I’m in so much pain inside 
- but still it’s so beautiful
